{"type":"message","id":"41bf99dc","parentId":"934a515d","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:51:23.962Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Today is June 1, 2026. The latest ID is COMPOSE-20260601-0005, so the next ID should be COMPOSE-20260601-0006.\n\nNow let me prepare the MiniMax API call. I need to:\n\n1. Style: 诡异又可爱，带点电子音和童谣感\n2. Mood: 既诡异又可爱\n3. Lyrics: No explicit lyrics provided, so lyrics_optimizer: true, AI auto-write lyrics\n4. is_instrumental: false (since there's a specific character/story, lyrics would make sense)\n\nLet me prepare the prompt for the API. I'll craft a detailed prompt that captures the essence of the description.\n\nThe prompt description: \"6月1日将近，诡异降临之夜，胆小的小萝莉戴猫耳猫尾穿小白袜系项圈，24小时陪聊驱散恐惧。曲风：诡异又可爱，带点电子音和童谣感。\"\n\nLet me call the MiniMax API.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_humvAauEF79WRohvVfGj2633","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/compose && \\\nNEXT_ID=\"COMPOSE-20260601-0006\" && \\\necho \"Next ID: $NEXT_ID\" && \\\nMINIMAX_KEY=\"sk-api…adXE\" && \\\ncurl -s -w \"\\n%{http_code}\" -X POST \"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $MINIMAX_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"music-2.6\",\n    \"prompt\": \"诡异又可爱的电子童谣，6月1日诡异降临之夜，胆小的小萝莉戴着猫耳猫尾、穿着小白袜系着项圈，24小时在线陪聊驱散恐惧。旋律带电子音效和童谣感，像是黑暗森林里传来的八音盒声，又带着一丝温暖和陪伴感。节奏轻快但略带悬疑色彩，适合夜晚独自聆听。\",\n    \"lyrics_optimizer\": true,\n    \"is_instrumental\": false,\n    \"output_format\": \"url\"\n  }' 2>&1","timeout":120},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/compose && \\\\\\nNEXT_ID=\\\"COMPOSE-20260601-0006\\\" && \\\\\\necho \\\"Next ID: $NEXT_ID\\\" && \\\\\\nMINIMAX_KEY=\\\"sk-api…adXE\\\" && \\\\\\ncurl -s -w \\\"\\\\n%{http_code}\\\" -X POST \\\"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/music_generation\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer $MINIMAX_KEY\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\