{"type":"message","id":"565161a3","parentId":"43e7a731","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:52:47.122Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to get the lyrics that the AI generated. The API response didn't include lyrics text, which means the AI auto-generated them (lyrics_optimizer was true). Let me check if there's a way to get the lyrics. Looking at the API response, it only returned the audio URL. The lyrics were generated server-side but not returned in the response.\n\nLet me check if MiniMax has a separate endpoint to retrieve lyrics or if the lyrics are embedded somehow. Actually, looking at the response more carefully, the data only contains audio URL and status. The lyrics were used for generation but aren't returned separately.\n\nSince I can't retrieve the exact lyrics from the API, I'll note that lyrics were AI-generated. Let me check the database to confirm.\n\nActually, looking at my database insert, I set lyrics to NULL. Since the AI generated lyrics but didn't return them, I should update this. Let me leave it as NULL for now since we don't have the actual lyrics text.\n\nNow I need to prepare the final output. The format should follow section 6.1:\n\n```\n🎵 新曲创作完成！\n────────────────\n🎼 曲名：{title}\n🎸 风格：{style}\n💖 情绪：{mood}\n⏱  时长：{duration}\n📝 歌词：\n{lyrics_preview}\n────────────────\n{field_audio_url} ← 点此播放\n{field_audio_file} ← 长按保存转发(下载后改.mp3)\n────────────────\n想换风格试试？ /重作曲 我想要摇滚风\n```\n\nWait, the cron says \"结果输出给汀桑（sender_id: 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204）\". Since this is an isolated cron session, the result will be delivered through the cron's announce delivery. Let me craft the reply.\n\nFor the field_audio_url and field_audio_file, based on the compose_function.md:\n- field_audio_url: the mp3 path for streaming - I should use the `<qqmedia>` tag format based on the qqbot-media skill\n- field_audio_file: the .mp3.bin for file sharing\n\nLooking at the qqbot-media skill, there should be a `<qqmedia>` tag. Let me check what format to use.\n\nActually, let me re-read section 6.1 more carefully. It says `{field_audio_url}` and `{field_audio_file}`. Since these are for QQ bot delivery, I should format them using the qqmedia tag.\n\nLooking at the qqbot-media skill description: \"Use <qqmedia> tags to send image, voice, video, or file attachments\"\n\nLet me use the media paths I set up.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xaMKKYCXcdFNja0cVQDu3443","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/qqbot-media/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":64,"output":637,"cacheRead":18816,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":578,"totalTokens":19517,"cost":{"input":0.00000896,"output":0.00017836000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000526848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000714168}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780249961235,"responseId":"129251fa-9bf3-444b-8b25-684e460539eb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b8f5a5c","parentId":"565161a3","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:52:47.192Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_xaMKKYCXcdFNja0cVQDu3443","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: qqbot-media\ndescription: QQBot rich media send and receive support. Use <qqmedia> tags to send image, voice, video, or file attachments, with the media type inferred from the file extension.\nmetadata: { \"openclaw\": { \"emoji\": \"📸\", \"requires\": { \"config\": [\"channels.qqbot\"] } } }\n---\n\n# QQBot 富媒体收发\n\n## 用法\n\n```\n<qqmedia>路径或URL</qqmedia>\n```\n\n系统根据文件扩展名自动识别类型并路由：\n\n- `.jpg/.png/.gif/.webp/.bmp` → 图片\n- `.silk/.wav/.mp3/.ogg/.aac/.flac` 等 → 语音\n- `.mp4/.mov/.avi/.mkv/.webm` 等 → 视频\n- 其他扩展名 → 文件\n- 无扩展名的 URL → 默认按图片处理\n\n## 接收媒体\n\n- 用户发来的**图片**自动下载到本地，路径在上下文【附件】中，可直接用 `<qqmedia>路径</qqmedia>` 回发\n- 用户发来的**语音**路径在上下文中；若有 STT 能力则优先转写\n\n## 规则\n\n1. **路径必须是绝对路径**（以 `/` 或 `http` 开头）\n2. **标签必须用开闭标签包裹路径**：`<qqmedia>路径</qqmedia>`\n3. **待发送的本地文件须落在 OpenClaw 媒体目录下**：生成、下载或复制出的文件应写入 **`~/.openclaw/media/qqbot/`**（或其子目录），再写进 `<qqmedia>`。不要只放在 `~/.openclaw/workspace/` 等工作区根目录——平台安全策略只允许从 `~/.openclaw/media/`（含 `media/qqbot`）等受信根路径上传，否则会拦截、发不出去。\n4. **文件大小上限**：图片 30MB / 视频 100MB / 文件 100MB / 语音 20MB\n5. **你有能力发送本地图片/文件**，直接用标签包裹路径即可，**不要说\"无法发送\"**\n6. 发送语音时不要重复语音中已朗读的文字\n7. 多个媒体用多个标签\n8. 以会话上下文中的能力说明为准（如未启用语音则不要发语音）\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780249967191}}
{"type":"message","id":"28c5d2b5","parentId":"1b8f5a5c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:52:49.048Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the format. The audio file is already in `~/.openclaw/media/qqbot/`. I need to format the response with `<qqmedia>` tags for both the mp3 (playable) and the .bin (file for saving).\n\nLet me compose the final response.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_wEdzhUoKrqaKcyPjY6GA9299","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/compose && \\\nsqlite3 compose.db \"SELECT lyrics FROM compositions WHERE id='COMPOSE-20260601-0006';\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/compose && \\\\\\nsqlite3 compose.db \\\"SELECT lyrics FROM compositions WHERE id='COMPOSE-20260601-0006';\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":603,"output":142,"cacheRead":19456,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":61,"totalTokens":20201,"cost":{"input":0.00008442000000000001,"output":0.000039760000000000006,"cacheRead":0.0005447679999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0006689479999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780249967202,"responseId":"c01f7ab3-6911-4e07-9a73-547dd33c2bdc"}}
