{"type":"message","id":"4a7d8c76","parentId":"387b6918","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:52:51.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The lyrics field is NULL since AI auto-generated them but didn't return them. Let me write a response as per the template.\n\nFor duration: 120 seconds = 2分00秒\n\nLet me compose the final output.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🎵 新曲创作完成！\n────────────────\n🎼 曲名：猫耳小萝莉的守夜童谣\n🎸 风格：诡异可爱电子童谣\n💖 情绪：诡异又可爱\n⏱  时长：2分00秒\n📝 歌词：\n（AI 自动生成 · 诡异童谣风）\n────────────────\n<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260601-0006.mp3</qqmedia> ← 点此播放\n<qqmedia>/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/COMPOSE-20260601-0006.mp3.bin</qqmedia> ← 长按保存转发（下载后改 .mp3）\n────────────────\n想换风格试试？ /重作曲 我想要摇滚风"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":119,"output":218,"cacheRead":20096,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":46,"totalTokens":20433,"cost":{"input":0.00001666,"output":0.00006104,"cacheRead":0.000562688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000640388}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780249969186,"responseId":"53fc18a9-f268-47aa-9b6a-653c067db443"}}
